{"title":"诗一首——听伍绍祖论武术有感","authors":["翟凤岗"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗一首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——听伍绍祖论武术有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翟凤岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武术环球领队人，太极一路荡风尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语惊四座成四论，情挚千重动千军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源自中华呈世界，类归体育更高深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健身竞技双得益，既重功夫尤重魂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}